    highlights: ["Two nights in Chefchaouen & Akchour hike option", "Fes medina full-day guided tour", "Two nights in Sahara desert camp", "Nomad Experience: Khamlia Gnawa music & Lake Merzouga", "Rissani ancient caravan souk", "Todra Gorge & Dades Valley", "Rose Valley & Skoura palmery", "Ait Benhaddou UNESCO kasbah", "Marrakech imperial sights", "Casablanca round trip"],
