    highlights: ["Two nights in Chefchaouen with Akchour hike option", "Fes medina & tanneries guided tour", "Erg Chebbi camel trek & Berber camp", "Todra Gorge canyon walls", "Rose Valley & Dades gorge kasbahs", "Ait Benhaddou UNESCO kasbah", "Marrakech Jemaa el-Fna & souks", "Essaouira overnight — beach, port & art galleries", "El Jadida Portuguese cistern", "Casablanca round trip"],
