    highlights: ["Arrival day in Casablanca at leisure", "Two nights in Chefchaouen & Akchour hike", "Fes medina full-day guided tour", "Sahara Erg Chebbi camel trek & camp", "Todra Gorge & Dades Valley kasbahs", "Ait Benhaddou UNESCO kasbah", "Three nights in Marrakech", "Optional hot air balloon over Marrakech", "Optional hammam, cooking class & rooftop dinner", "Essaouira coastal finale"],
